news.title: L&T sells three pre-leased floors in Powai office tower to National Realty for Rs 81 crore
news.para: The company sold this office with nearly 37,527 sq ft carpet area immediately after leasing it to CitiusTech Healthcare Technology at starting annual rent of Rs 7.40 crore.

news.title: Why 2.5 lakh flats' registries are stuck in Noida
news.para: For long, homebuyers had pinned hopes on the apex court judgment related to the rate of land dues, anticipating that builders will clear their dues as per the court order and the registry of flats will finally start.

news.title: Many haven't shifted to new flats yet, but Noida authority starts demolition of slums
news.para: The move comes nearly three years after the Authority allotted 2,064 newly-built flats in Sector 122 to slum residents under the jhuggi jhopri rehabilitation scheme.
